{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "6b153979-ad75-415d-899f-6193fb80b867", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6b153979-ad75-415d-899f-6193fb80b867@2.pkg/1772602105601/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602106160", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6b153979-ad75-415d-899f-6193fb80b867@2.pkg/1772602105601/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602106160"}, "identifier": "6b153979-ad75-415d-899f-6193fb80b867", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;江山如此多娇，引无数英雄竞折腰&rdquo;，承上启下，将全词连接得天衣无缝。&ldquo;江山如此多娇&rdquo;承上，总括上片的写景，对&ldquo;北国风光&rdquo;作总评；&ldquo;引无数英雄竞折腰&rdquo;启下，展开对历代英雄的评论，抒发诗人的抱负。</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;江山如此多娇，引无数英雄竞折腰&rdquo;一句在全词中的作用是</span><span>（　　）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "“江山如此多娇，引无数英雄竞折腰”一句在全词中的作用是（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/6b153979-ad75-415d-899f-6193fb80b867@2.pkg/item.json?v=1752739160422", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>承接上文，进一步地赞美祖国的大好河山。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>引起下文，为具体评价历史人物作辅垫。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>开启下文，写出历史上许多英雄人物为祖国的大好河山而倾倒。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>承上启下，再次赞美祖国的大好河山，又指出历史人物为祖国山河倾倒，为下文评论历史人物作铺垫。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;江山如此多娇，引无数英雄竞折腰&rdquo;一句在全词中的作用是</span><span>（　　）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "$RE0200", "5036342748", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "PS003", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "6b153979-ad75-415d-899f-6193fb80b867", "global_title": {"zh-C